{{Top|leg}}
'''Glaze cakes''' were a sweet dessert. The [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]] was carrying a load of glaze cakes when she crashed her starship ''[[Pok's Demise]]'' on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. Some local [[Scurrier/Legends|scurriers]] had been attracted to the smell of the cakes on her ship and ate them; they ended up gnawing on many of her ship systems as well.<ref name="sot">{{GalaxyCite|10|Sandbound on Tatooine}}</ref>

Saying that something would be "''a piece of glaze cake''" indicated that it was going to be an easy job.<ref name="idc">''[[Imperial Double-Cross]]''</ref>

